        <div class="col-row">
            






<div class="article pbl right-col size3of4 cf">



        <h1 class="header-skin header-structure">Leadership and Governance</h1>


    <div class="relative ">


            <div class="content-block">

<p class="lead">Around 50 full-time members of staff (including support staff) and nearly 200 visiting specialist tutors work at the Conservatoire. This means that for roughly every two students there is one member of staff.</p>
<p>The vast majority of our tutors are active professional musicians, dividing their time between performing or composing and teaching. All are dedicated and experienced musicians with a passion for inspiring and training the next generation of professionals.</p>
<p>For a full list of staff in each department or area, as well as selected biographies, please go to the <a href="/pme/conservatoire/departments">Music Departments and Tutors</a> page, or the <a href="/conservatoire/acting/staff-and-facilities">Acting staff</a>. </p>
<p>You can also <a href="/conservatoire/about-us/meet-our-heads-of-department">meet our Heads of Department</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Royal Birmingham Conservatoire President:</strong> Sir Simon Rattle CBE</p>
<p><strong>Royal Birmingham Conservatoire Vice-President:</strong> Peter Donohoe CBE</p>
<h4>Principal's Office:</h4>
<p>Principal: <a href="/conservatoire/about-us/birmingham-conservatoire-tutors-and-staff/stephen-maddock-obe">Stephen Maddock</a><br>Vice Principal (Music): <a href="/conservatoire/about-us/birmingham-conservatoire-tutors-and-staff/shirley-thompson">Shirley Thompson (currently on research leave)<br></a>Vice Principal (Acting): <a href="/conservatoire/about-us/birmingham-conservatoire-tutors-and-staff/stephen-simms">Stephen Simms<br></a>Interim Vice Principal (Music): <a href="mailto:simon.hall@bcu.ac.uk">Simon Hall</a><br>Interim Vice Principal (Music): <a href="mailto:duncan.fielden@bcu.ac.uk">Duncan Fielden</a><br><span>Associate Principal (International): </span><a href="/conservatoire/research/research-staff/lamberto-coccioli">Lamberto Coccioli<br></a><span>Executive PA to Principal: </span><a href="mailto:andrea.cox@bcu.ac.uk">Andrea Cox<br></a><span>Administrative Officer (Principal's Office): </span><a href="mailto:judy.francis@bcu.ac.uk">Judy Francis</a></p>
<h4>Junior Conservatoire:</h4>
<p>Head of RBC Junior Conservatoire: <a href="mailto:Timothy.English@bcu.ac.uk">Tim English</a><br> Junior Conservatoire Administrators: Mia Walters</p>
<h4>Professional Services Teams:</h4>
<p>Operations Manager: <a href="mailto:jamie.suttle@bcu.ac.uk">Jamie Suttle</a><br> Academic Administration Team Leader: <a href="mailto:Rakhi.Sahota@bcu.ac.uk">Rakhi Sahota</a><br><span>Professional Engagements Manager: <a href="mailto:lynsey.hopkinson@bcu.ac.uk">Lynsey Hopkinson</a></span><br> International Coordinator: <a href="mailto:ruth.wootton@bcu.ac.uk">Ruth Wootton</a><br> Conservatoire Librarian: <a href="mailto:francis.firth@bcu.ac.uk">Francis Firth</a><br> RBC Facilities Supervisor: <a href="mailto:ian.pountney@bcu.ac.uk">Ian Pountney</a></p>
<h4>Events Office:</h4>
<p>Venues Manager: <a href="mailto:Libby.Surplice@bcu.ac.uk">Libby Surplice</a><br> Events Marketing Manager: <a href="mailto:Andy.Roberts@bcu.ac.uk ">Andy Roberts<br><br></a></p>
<p><strong>General Contact</strong>: <a href="mailto:Conservatoire@bcu.ac.uk">Conservatoire@bcu.ac.uk</a></p>
<p><a class="button" href="/pme/conservatoire/departments">Music Departments and Tutors</a></p>
<p><a class="button" href="/conservatoire/acting/staff-and-facilities">Acting staff</a></p>
            </div>

